The only way those
things can happen

00:15:48.870 --> 00:15:52.680 align:middle line:84%
is because life has lost its
specialness, its significance.

00:15:52.680 --> 00:15:55.220 align:middle line:84%
It's this thinking that
is leading us, as I said,

