00:16:44.900 --> 00:16:49.090 align:middle line:84%
In 1962, there was a woman,
her name was Rachel Carson.

00:16:49.090 --> 00:16:51.140 align:middle line:10%
She was one of the
first environmentalists

00:16:51.140 --> 00:16:52.780 align:middle line:10%
in the modern world.

00:16:52.780 --> 00:16:55.760 align:middle line:84%
I have so much respect,
and I revere her work

00:16:55.760 --> 00:16:57.103 align:middle line:90%
