00:16:57.103 --> 00:16:58.520 align:middle line:84%
You may be familiar
with her work.

00:16:58.520 --> 00:17:01.820 align:middle line:10%
She wrote a book that was
titled, "Silent Spring,"

00:17:01.820 --> 00:17:05.089 align:middle line:10%
and it was the warning
sign-- the red light

00:17:05.089 --> 00:17:07.609 align:middle line:10%
to the dangers at that time
of the pesticide that was

00:17:07.609 --> 00:17:10.760 align:middle line:10%
