00:17:10.760 --> 00:17:14.930 align:middle line:84%
And if you're in my age
bracket, you may remember DDT--

00:17:14.930 --> 00:17:18.410 align:middle line:84%
I remember living in the
Midwest in the summer months.

00:17:18.410 --> 00:17:21.319 align:middle line:10%
Trucks would drive up and
down the street spraying

00:17:21.319 --> 00:17:24.470 align:middle line:10%
this cloud, this
gaseous cloud of DDT

00:17:24.470 --> 00:17:26.240 align:middle line:10%
into the gutters
along the street

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:28.640 align:middle line:10%
to keep mosquitoes
from breeding.

00:17:28.640 --> 00:17:30.290 align:middle line:10%
And while they
were doing that, we

00:17:30.290 --> 00:17:31.880 align:middle line:10%
