said during that time,

00:17:55.520 --> 00:17:57.340 align:middle line:84%
she made a statement
in that book

00:17:57.340 --> 00:18:00.260 align:middle line:84%
and I want to share it with you,
because it is as potent today

00:18:00.260 --> 00:18:02.000 align:middle line:90%
as it was the 1960s.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:05.100 align:middle line:84%
Listen to the wisdom of Rachel
Carson and what she says.

00:18:05.100 --> 00:18:09.320 align:middle line:84%
She says, "We only destroy
what we don't value,

00:18:09.320 --> 00:18:13.040 align:middle line:84%
and we can only value
what we understand."

00:18:13.040 --> 00:18:13.840 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

