us at an unprecedented rate.

00:18:19.267 --> 00:18:20.725 align:middle line:84%
And if we're honest
with ourselves,

00:18:20.725 --> 00:18:23.830 align:middle line:90%
you know and I know it's true.

00:18:23.830 --> 00:18:26.860 align:middle line:84%
It's happening and it continues,
and it's only happening

00:18:26.860 --> 00:18:29.140 align:middle line:90%
because of a way of thinking.

00:18:29.140 --> 00:18:31.360 align:middle line:84%
I keep coming back to this,
